description: This Chainlink VRF common Sakura purrs with a rating of 28, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 28, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, 8 for East, 1 for South, and Box for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/10281-78140-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [28 Votes, Common]
